[[File:Rebel_Major_General.jpg|thumb|A Major General within the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]].]]
'''Major General''' was a military rank. [[Carner]] was a Major General of the Imperial Army stationed on [[Garos IV]].<ref name="AGoH">{{JournalCite|1|A Glimmer of Hope}}</ref> [[Freja Covell]] was promoted to Major General by [[Captain/Legends|Captain]] [[Gilad Pellaeon/Legends|Gilad Pellaeon]] and later commanded ''[[Chimaera/Legends|Chimaera]]''{{'s}} entire Army force under [[Grand Admiral/Legends|Grand Admiral]] [[Mitth'raw'nuruodo/Legends|Thrawn's]] direct command.<ref name="Dark Force Rising Sourcebook">''[[Dark Force Rising Sourcebook]]''</ref>

The rank of Major General was also used in other military forces, including those of the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] and [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]]: [[Eldo Davip]] was promoted from [[Commander/Legends|Commander]] to this rank after the [[Battle of Borleias (Yuuzhan Vong War; Second)|Battle of Borleias]].<ref name="The New Jedi Order: The Unifying Force">''[[The New Jedi Order: The Unifying Force]]''</ref>

